    "95fd7dd5-6e0c-4ff0-b13e-91d7f2177108": {
      "type": "text-only",
      "settings": {
        "large_text": "Our Story",
        "small_text": "<p>Crafter’s Companion started life as a big dream in Sara Davies’ university bedroom. It was here that she had a light bulb moment, about a ground-breaking product which could create envelopes for handmade cards, and The Enveloper was born!<\/p><p>Sixteen years (and lots of hard work) later, we’ve grown our product range from one exciting papercraft tool to thousands of crafting must-haves including stamps, dies and die-cutting machines, embossing folders, card and more to enhance your creative journey and bolster stashes across the world!<\/p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": "",
        "left_align": true
      }
    },
