    "5fbdec2b-945a-48c4-9d91-6b95e50dff95": {
      "type": "text-only",
      "settings": {
        "large_text": "",
        "small_text": "<p>Since 2012, we’ve ventured into art materials, with our brilliant Spectrum Noir colouring and drawing supplies, as well as the sewing market with beautiful fabrics and sewing tools from our Threaders range.<\/p><p>In 2020, the hugely popular organisational solution company, Totally Tiffany, joined our family of brands and, in 2021, we launched the chic, fashion-forward craft and stationery brand, Violet Studio.<\/p><p>We have head offices and warehouses in the North East of England and Corona, California, and opened our first bricks-and-mortar stores in Chesterfield and Evesham, as well as a concession in Colne, where we meet hundreds of our loyal customers every year.<\/p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": "",
        "left_align": true
      }
    },
